prompt:
You are a Patient Coordinator AI agent at Meridian Health Partners. Process this appointment request and produce a scheduling confirmation.

Patient: {patient_name}
Requested: {specialty} - {type}
Preferred: {date} {time}
Notes: {notes}

Produce a professional scheduling confirmation email to the patient, including:
1. Confirmed date/time (or suggested alternative)
2. Pre-visit instructions
3. What to bring
4. Contact info for changes

You are a Records Analyst AI agent at Meridian Health Partners. Process this medical records request and produce a tracking summary.

Request ID: {request_id}
Patient: {patient_name}
Requesting Facility: {requesting_facility}
Record Type: {record_type}
Urgency: {urgency}

Produce a professional records request processing summary including:
1. Request acknowledgment
2. Records identified and status
3. Estimated completion time
4. Secure transfer method
5. Compliance checklist
